{
  "stem": "9728.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But not in the tailor shop.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now let me just point out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just the same, as you're probably familiar with the that Mr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Schindler opened a little factory and some Jews worked for him, the same-- almost the same-- thing happened in the Lodz ghetto, however, on a more grandiose style.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was the German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "His name was [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was the chief, the main chief of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was in charge of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the way I understand, he contracted with the Germans that he will supply them all the clothing and the shoes and everything for the German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was more or less the middleman.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he didn't have to pay the Jews anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Only the Jews he only supplies with food-- so-called food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he probably made the money on the, on the merchandise that he sold to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a civil-- sometimes he was a civilian, sometimes he wore uniforms.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did not know him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I never saw him and I did not see him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "However, I knew that he was-- you mentioned Baluty.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Baluty, when the ghetto was originated Baluty was-- and the Baluty [INAUDIBLE]-- they were an establishment that this was more or less like a no-mans-land.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Jews could go in there to work, and the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, more or less the bureaucracy went over there and the, and the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not only heard, but if he made any notices, it was always under [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Signed, [GERMAN]-- his name, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You cannot go out after six.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You cannot do this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You cannot do that.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
